title: Louie Gohmert
added: On January 5, 2021 Cutler from [[Pennsylvania]] filed a 295 page Emergency Expedited Petition for [[En banc]] hearing with time stamped evidence from 12APR2018 of [[Robert Torres]] that the result from [[Josh Shapiro]] is [[Mail Fraud]]. On 12APR2018 [[Robert Torres]] issued an ORDER that all voting methods must have a hard copy receipt available, paid for with federal funds. The DROP BOXES in Pennsylvania failed to have a Hard Copy receipt available, and therefore all votes via drop boxes must be considered illegal and excluded.<ref>www.pacer.gov</ref>
